       <HR>
       <FONT size="+1">Stable ointment containing acetylsalicylic acid
</FONT><BR>
       <BR><CENTER><b>Abstract</b></CENTER>
       <p> A substantially anhydrous stable ointment containing <B><I>Aspirin</I></B> which is
     characterized in using gelation hydrocarbon and/or vaseline as a base.
     The ointment is superior in stability and can be stored for a long term.
</p>
       <HR>
