<BR><BR>INDUSTRIAL APPLICABILITY
<BR><BR> The ointments of the present invention containing Aspirin can be stored stably Aspirin for a long term in form of the substantially anhydrous ointment containing hydrocarbon gel and/or vaseline as a base.
